        <head xml:id="la30px-bbb145-Hd1e104">Proposition 24</head>
        <p xml:id="la30px-bbb145-d1e106"> Proposition 24 </p>
        <p xml:id="la30px-bbb145-d1e111">
          Whoever dares to persuade others that evangelism is best
          begun with war, goes directly against divine law.30 Greater is their audacity and temerity
          than that of the one putting themself naked before a hundred fierce lions and tigers. They
          have poorly understood the different categories of infidels that one must understand, in
          order to determine against whom conquests are to be made. They have not learned caridad,31
          which so much charged us Christ, and their sin is inexpiable. Therefore the hard justice
          which is to come to them is of most just cause. 
        </p>
